Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没能去成啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.71,0:00:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.49,0:00:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有遗憾就不能说享受了夏天呢
