Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  这不是旅行这只是留宿派对  对吧 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  很吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.62,0:03:26.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  千秋也醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:29.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太吵了睡不着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好热啊又不是旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以入睡的夜晚  由我提供鬼故事服务您意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以入睡的夜晚有冷气的服务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那种服务  客人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服务好差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.19,0:03:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事什么的蠢死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧睡觉吧  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是害怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.59,0:03:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来玩吧  鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐也参加
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲鬼故事来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么由内田开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.09,0:04:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  从我开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.91,0:04:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.21,0:04:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久很久以前在某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是传说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:30.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的鬼故事就想吓到我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个  该冬马了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒的冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔的洗衣机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说哪个？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:48.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身边的道具来引发恐惧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.45,0:04:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想增加点有趣的元素还特意让我们三选一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选项只有家电啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么选吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:59.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸尘器吗  选了吸尘器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  恐怖的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这是个什么样的故事来着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是虚张声势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.93,0:05:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有标题很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  标题很可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个故事我知道哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.28,0:05:20.51,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  不用勉强也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  这回拜托你了  内田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.25,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看现在已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:21.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐～怖～的～吸～尘～器～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某对新婚夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买了新家用的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那个夜晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妻子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我新娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新娘子哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事  我的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.48,0:05:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天买回来的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.14,0:05:51.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天买回来的吸尘器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.43,0:05:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了不会后悔？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.49,0:06:02.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天买回来的吸尘器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是麸皮做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.32,0:06:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天买回来了个麸皮做的吸尘器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:27.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  麸皮的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,360)\fad(0,500)}恐怖的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:33.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注：「今日（きょう）お麩（ふ）の掃除機」发音\N与「恐怖（きょうふ）の掃除機」类似
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:33.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,360)\fad(500,0)}今天、麸皮的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖的吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是冷笑话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个故事和恐怖的味噌汁相似啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  麸皮的味噌汁的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼故事怎么办啊  鬼故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.14,0:06:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  到底是什么样的故事来着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:55.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是收到了吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:58.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那个故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得是吸尘器里发出了呻吟声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把结局说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不应该有更厉害的结局么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对不对  呻吟声就是结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登场的不是老夫老妻么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.31,0:07:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家各执一词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:17.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呻吟声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从哪发出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲鬼怪故事就会招来鬼怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说吸尘器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.86,0:07:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.11,0:07:35.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吓我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.58,0:07:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  是梦啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是春香的呻吟声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什么可怕的梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个非常可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什么很沉的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-94,0:00:-8.-94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不说鬼故事了  各自爆料自己喜欢的男性吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么从谁开始讲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么按年龄大小来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南…南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-94,0:00:-8.-94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都已经下半学期了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种高温到底要持续到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的秋老虎真久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.94,0:08:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早～上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.09,0:08:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是新学期没有精神啊  精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么热你也这么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上就试着用左手吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右脚鞋子反着穿等等分散了注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算把炎热忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘掉了的炎热一下子就把我击倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们要负责让我凉快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:14.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  放学回家给你买冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.01,0:09:18.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圭子  不能这样惯她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,免费让你变得凉快不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过啊  好像长了蛀牙不能吃冰淇淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我蛀牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.17,0:09:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给圭子了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去交换有点难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在在控制甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子有点不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经有个了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个中奖棒怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是还给夏奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.68,0:10:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  好像很精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼痛和炎热已经忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.79,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得中的奖  还是还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊  好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.51,0:10:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好蛀牙前先收着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日的茂草  武士们留下的梦的点滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:38.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}元俳句出自松尾芭蕉「夏草や 兵どもが 夢の跡」\N比喻功名利禄只在旦夕之间转瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.29,0:10:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别抄袭别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就知道是我中到的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}夏日的茂草  强者们留下的梦的点滴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  到底抄袭了几次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:56.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  这个是去年中到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖小到收起来后就会忘掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈给的礼物？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.66,0:11:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.42,0:11:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.33,0:11:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去看牙医吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-94,0:00:-8.-94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家斗恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.93,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}沙漠里倒下  篇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,200)}南家斗恶龙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:22.92,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,500)}绿洲发现？！篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-94,0:00:-8.-94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.10,0:11:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啊  三宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.39,0:11:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健叔  在喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸说  酒在夏天会很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过据说很苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦中有美味
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  酒要20岁以后才能喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.66,0:11:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  这个给健叔拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是毛豆啊  也有我的份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有我也会自己偷拿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…为什么打我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷吃毛豆是这么重的罪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.69,0:12:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…因为有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.39,0:12:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蚊子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.34,0:12:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  这不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是蚊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.16,0:12:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.50,0:12:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干…干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你擅自吃了我的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便吃妹妹的冰淇淋有什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.02,0:12:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是把中奖棒给你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得60日元的棒冰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.40,0:12:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和含税共计284日元的高级冰激凌相提并论吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.61,0:12:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许再使用暴力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有蚊子  一只大蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.89,0:13:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  是蚊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宫同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健叔是放假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是带薪休假哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么是带薪休假？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是休假  但也能拿到工资哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸说的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有工资
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说现在健是既有钱拿又有休假咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是赢家嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.43,0:13:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我先去给健叔揉揉肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前南家住宿旅行的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的长篇故事害得我睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么补偿我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的旅行？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得大家都互相说着话然后就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说啊  要是把斑马的斑马线去掉应该就变成马了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是斑马是白的  所以会变成白马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  你的故事会很长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.23,0:13:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我困了就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你困了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不困
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.02,0:13:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一下厕所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是条纹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我把这段讲完了再去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事很长的是夏奈吧  我可是很困的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:20.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛打我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:22.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一只带条纹的蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  下雨的时候你对我泼水了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:33.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是说之前梅雨的时候吗  亏你还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.21,0:14:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有一只眼神很凶的蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了冬马  有蚊子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没有  吉野身上没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂等一下  我到底是为了什么被打
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…总觉得有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫总觉得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:09.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蚊子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有什么蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  就是有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想打我吧  老实承认吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承认了的话还能打你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:32.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健被压扁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:33.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.75,0:15:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有一只又大又带条纹眼神很凶的蚊子…在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:43.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  健叔已经睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.07,0:15:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被蚊子叮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-84,0:00:-8.-84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿健没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能变成这样的大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丽子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都订好餐厅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  这家伙放假了还来我们家就说明…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天还是对他好点吧  就今天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-84,0:00:-8.-84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然已经不早了  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.57,0:16:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好夏奈  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健那家伙  今天也没事干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貌似是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我也给他上茶了  也算招待过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就随便对付下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样老是来还真烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.49,0:17:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都听得见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来春香呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.10,0:17:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去买东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.97,0:17:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那午饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:16.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.12,0:17:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要饿死我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:20.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己做点什么不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经快饿到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  健你之前吃了春香做的类似毛豆的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着我的眼睛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:37.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的侄女正饿着肚子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为叔叔你不觉得自己应该做点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叔叔  是表哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的侄女啊  就只想吃一点点好吃的午餐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:49.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛背过身去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.87,0:17:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的侄女作为一个日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到有东西在转就想吃一种食物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦千秋  你指的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在转的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:04.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:08.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  没想到会请我们吃寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不巧的时候碰上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是正巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  有钱人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉有钱人  人变多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  虽说是没关系…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.66,0:18:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过人均1000日元哦  要遵守啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间店有从每碟100日元至500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共分5个等级
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白碟  100日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.14,0:18:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好看的带镶边的碟子  200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来有那么点高档的碟子  300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,颇有厚重感的碟子  400日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是看起来很豪华的碟子  500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有一千日元就能吃的很饱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:03.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一不小心就会超过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.23,0:19:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的解说  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  请给我两碟金枪鱼大肥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.94,0:19:12.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真厉害  上来就点两碟500日元的结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要蛋卷  蒸蛋  鲑鱼子  还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是蛋呢  反正你就是各种蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:21.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才吃的那个叫不出名字的白色食物  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.89,0:19:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹牙的  脆脆的  一瞬间就化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白身鱼的寿司有很多种呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是吃了哪一种呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  我用鱿鱼和你的甜虾交换着吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.29,0:19:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在是100  200  300日元的各一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共计300日元对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦千秋  计算有问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该是很聪明的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  我的甜虾和你的扇贝交换下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是两碟100  一碟200  两碟300
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:02.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了这么多还只花了500日元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  千秋再算一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  我用扇贝和你的鲑鱼子交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.48,0:20:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野  我用鲑鱼子和你最后的金枪鱼大肥交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  终于换到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共7000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.02,0:20:25.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去之前让我再想一想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.94,0:20:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是一个人1000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最后却花了7000
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.69,0:20:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7000？六个人应该是6000吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  千秋的碟子有点不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后有连续两碟500的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光那两碟就1000了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.29,0:20:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不守规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不是少算了一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是藤冈的份！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.79,0:20:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.69,0:20:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看它嘴边粘着饭粒就是证据
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:56.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:20:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.92,0:21:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.05,0:21:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  正好碰到真希和淳子所以说了一会话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:16.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服哦  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.50,0:21:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋真乖啊  我现在就去做午饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经吃过寿司当午饭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:23.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寿司？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:27.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健带我们去的  春香也一起来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.51,0:21:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说春香姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.70,0:21:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去买午饭的材料…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我们去吃寿司吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.23,0:21:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-8.-84,0:00:-8.-84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
